6ï¸âƒ£ Best Practices for Database Management
ğŸ”¹ Use Indexing to speed up searches.
ğŸ”¹ Backup your database regularly.
ğŸ”¹ Normalize data to avoid duplication.
ğŸ”¹ Secure your database (Use encryption & authentication).
ğŸ”¹ Optimize queries (Use JOIN instead of multiple queries).
